<i>noun</i>: 맞바람 [맏빠람] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>맞바람 [맏빠람]</dt><br>
<dd>1. crosswind</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 물체의 진행 방향과 반대 방향으로 부는 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>Wind blowing in the direction opposite the direction of a person or thing moving.</dd><br>
<dd>2. crosswind</dd><br>
<dd>양쪽에서 마주 부는 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>Winds blowing against each other from opposite directions.</dd><br>
<dd>3. revenge affair</dd><br>
<dd>외도하는 배우자에 대응하여 하는 외도.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of having an extramarital affair in reprisal for one's spouse having such an affair.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>